[
  {
    "front": "In the winter time.",
    "back": "في وقت الشتاء.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "When deep snow lay on the ground.",
    "back": "حين كان الثلج العميق يغطي الأرض.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "A poor boy was forced to go out on a sledge.",
    "back": "أُجبر ولد فقير على الخروج بمزلجة.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "To fetch wood.",
    "back": "لجلب الحطب.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "When he had gathered it together.",
    "back": "وعندما جمعه.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "And packed it.",
    "back": "ورتبه.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "He wished not to go home at once.",
    "back": "رغب ألا يعود للبيت فوراً.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "As he was so frozen with cold.",
    "back": "لأنه كان متجمداً من البرد.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "But to light a fire.",
    "back": "بل أن يشعل ناراً.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "And warm himself a little.",
    "back": "ويدفئ نفسه قليلاً.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "So he scraped away the snow.",
    "back": "فكشط الثلج.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "And as he was thus clearing the ground.",
    "back": "وبينما كان ينظف الأرض بهذه الطريقة.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "He found a tiny, gold key.",
    "back": "وجد مفتاحاً ذهبياً صغيراً جداً.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "Hereupon he thought.",
    "back": "حينئذ فكر.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "Where the key was.",
    "back": "حيث يوجد المفتاح.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "The lock must be also.",
    "back": "فلا بد أن يوجد القفل أيضاً.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "And dug in the ground.",
    "back": "فحفر في الأرض.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "And found an iron chest.",
    "back": "ووجد صندوقاً حديدياً.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "If the key does but fit it!",
    "back": "لو أن المفتاح يطابق القفل فقط!",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "Thought he.",
    "back": "فكر.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "No doubt there are precious things.",
    "back": "فلا شك أن هناك أشياء ثمينة.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "In that little box.",
    "back": "في ذلك الصندوق الصغير.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "He searched.",
    "back": "بحث.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "But no keyhole was there.",
    "back": "لكن لم يكن هناك ثقب للمفتاح.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "At last he discovered one.",
    "back": "وأخيراً اكتشف واحداً.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "But so small.",
    "back": "لكنه كان صغيراً جداً.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "That it was hardly visible.",
    "back": "لدرجة أنه بالكاد كان مرئياً.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "He tried it.",
    "back": "جربه.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "And the key fitted it exactly.",
    "back": "فطابقه المفتاح تماماً.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "Then he turned it once round.",
    "back": "ثم أداره دورة واحدة.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "And now we must wait.",
    "back": "والآن علينا أن ننتظر.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "Until he has quite unlocked it.",
    "back": "حتى يفتحه تماماً.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "And opened the lid.",
    "back": "ويرفع الغطاء.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "And then we shall learn.",
    "back": "وعندها سنعرف.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  },
  {
    "front": "What wonderful things were lying in that box.",
    "back": "ما هي الأشياء العجيبة التي كانت موجودة في ذلك الصندوق.",
    "frontDir": "ltr",
    "backDir": "rtl",
    "learned": false
  }
]
